{"tid":924683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰】陳家強：不相信中國捱不起來　稱關稅太高美國捱不住","createTime":"2018-12-02T09:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T11:49:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"21e52de77786b7264669655e62e7dcd34eff99ce","tid":924683,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:47:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181202/s00001/45e30c03ed97c2ac0b502b8e2e417d81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181202%2Fs00001%2F45e30c03ed97c2ac0b502b8e2e417d81.jpg&h=8009cfdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰持續，財經事務及庫務局前局長陳家強接受無綫訪問時指，不相信關稅會令中國捱不住，反而若關稅太高，美國捱不住。<br />\n<br />\n陳家強於訪問中，被問到中美貿易戰是否有轉圜餘地，他稱「如果（美國）和中國談不合攏，其實（美國）贏不了什麼，所以不一定沒彎轉，（美國）應該希望有一個協議」。<br />\n<br />\n但他提到，「是否有這個關稅（就）令中國捱不起來呢，我又不相信&hellip;&hellip;有時也不需要太害怕，因為增加關稅到太高地步，其實美國捱不住的。我們中國當然也會受傷，但美國也捱不住的，所以等着瞧」。<br />\n<br />\n不過陳家強預料，即使談判失敗，港股下跌也會「有個底」，「（股市）不會和現在的水平差太遠。因為股市最近已經跌了很多，這兩個月因為貿易戰跌了不少，就算再跌也會有支持位」。"},{"pid":"c1fb820860cb08349b85df9701909768f154b63d","tid":924683,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/1951324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F1951324&d=Qx2xuUP7W70gsE4E%2BeShXZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=d3e7dded\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/1951324</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2018年9月22日</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>陳家強料美「靠嚇」 關稅未必調高至25%</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2018/09/22/1951324_c201e2d8e832e1455bd8eeda406af771.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F1951324_c201e2d8e832e1455bd8eeda406af771.jpg&h=f2b5aaf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n財經事務及庫務局前局長、科大商學院兼任教授陳家強出席一個電台節目時表示，中美貿易戰本質是兩國角力，相信美國會調高中國商品關稅，但未必真的會增至25%。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，因為全面增加關稅不但影響兩國關係，亦會對美國消費者造成影響，現在只是想「靠嚇」迫中國談判。<br />\n<br />\n不過，陳家強批評美國總統特朗普不懂經濟，無知卻有自信，不肯認輸；而中國面對缺乏戰略性思維的對手，難以談判，沒有選擇之下惟有不談判。<br />\n<br />\n陳家強認為，中國目前最好的應對態度，可能是與美國保持關係，希望磨擦不要過度升溫，同時與美國內部不同利益團體接觸，希望將來特朗普不在白宮時會有較好的結果。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，雖然中國經濟有減慢跡象，但指出口佔整體經濟比例低，認為貿易戰對中國整體經濟影響不太大。至於本港經濟受投資影響較大，相信中美貿易戰帶來的影響亦有限。"},{"pid":"c45ec04b91a6345448927692a983b5e60aa71886","tid":924683,"uid":35430,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:51:08.000Z","msg":"冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該支持中國企硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b7e60155ec722ce38c8385d1c77a7565adf537","tid":924683,"uid":153778,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:52:00.000Z","msg":"條友老幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港已經冇乜人記得佢，去到外國識佢老鼠咩，佢做過生意咩？佢上過位做老頂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教人做美國總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c919f028b03ff934d96d3f3b6aa803b3053059","tid":924683,"uid":138752,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:52:58.000Z","msg":"佢無錯喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那蝗食一年樹皮都得 <br />\n美國佬食一日都未必得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支持企硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95ef3fa3bcc2d0a898e041023cd7fc685b7322e","tid":924683,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:54:31.000Z","msg":"中國已成最大贏家"},{"pid":"53012f22b4a272544c53349a08081a3f665a200f","tid":924683,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bab7579672133ffe0d861f2923c31215b9211a3","tid":924683,"uid":35870,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"不過，陳家強批評美國總統特朗普不懂經濟，無知卻有自信，不肯認輸<br />\n<br />\nTrump不懂經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你應該不懂政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2283d109280591826c01078e169e952d99d5a448","tid":924683,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c1fb820860cb08349b85df9701909768f154b63d","tid":924683,"uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T09:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/1951324\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F1951324&d=Qx2xuUP7W70gsE4E%2BeShXZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=d3e7dded\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/1951324</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><s